component.illusobjdesc:
Eight figures sit or kneel in a row beneath the host of angels.  Third from the right, a male shepherd sits on a stone with 
                  his right leg bent back.  He has long hair, and his gown has a hood which is not drawn up.  He is seen from behind with his head bent back; 
                  he looks toward the angels above.  His arms are bent with his hands raised palms out (away from the viewer).
